---
<Layout title="Marketing, Auctions and Selling Methods | Daniel Gierach Property" description="How to run a sales campaign, choose between auction and private treaty, handle offers, and work effectively with a real estate agent in Brisbane." schema={clusterSchema}>

<article style="background:var(--color-surface-0);min-height:100vh;">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <div style="background:#0a0806;padding:8rem 0 3.5rem;">
    <div class="max-w-[1100px] mx-auto px-8">
      <a href="/insights" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:0.65rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);text-decoration:none;margin-bottom:2rem;transition:color 0.2s;"
        onmouseover="this.style.color='#f5d07a'" onmouseout="this.style.color='rgba(240,236,228,0.6)'">
        &larr; All Articles
      </a>
      <span style="display:block;font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:0.6rem;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#f5d07a;margin-bottom:1rem;">Topic Guide &middot; 32 Articles</span>
      <h1 style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:clamp(2rem,5vw,3.25rem);font-weight:400;color:#f0ece4;line-height:1.12;letter-spacing:-0.02em;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
        Marketing, Auctions and Selling Methods
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:58ch;">
        How your property is marketed and which sale method you choose can meaningfully affect your result. This guide covers campaign structure, auction versus private treaty, how to handle offers, how to choose and change your agent, and what off-market really means.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Article Grid -->
  <div style="padding:3.5rem 0 5rem;background:var(--color-base);">
    <div class="max-w-[1100px] mx-auto px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
        {articles.map(a => (
          <a href={`/insights/${a.slug}`}
            style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid rgba(28,25,23,0.1);padding:2rem;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1rem;text-decoration:none;transition:background 0.25s,border-color 0.25s,transform 0.3s,box-shadow 0.3s;position:relative;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 1px 4px rgba(28,25,23,0.05);"
            onmouseover="this.style.background='#f2efe9';this.style.borderColor='rgba(196,145,42,0.3)';this.style.transform='translateY(-4px)';this.style.boxShadow='0 10px 28px rgba(28,25,23,0.09)'"
            onmouseout="this.style.background='#ffffff';this.style.borderColor='rgba(28,25,23,0.1)';this.style.transform='translateY(0)';this.style.boxShadow='0 1px 4px rgba(28,25,23,0.05)'"
          >
            <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:3px;background:#f5d07a;"></div>
            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;padding-top:0.25rem;">
              <span style="font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:0.55rem;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:0.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#f5d07a;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.35rem;">
                <span style="width:5px;height:5px;border-radius:50%;background:#f5d07a;flex-shrink:0;"></span>
                Sellers
              </span>
            </div>
            <div style="flex:1;">
              <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:400;color:#1c1917;line-height:1.3;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">{a.title}</h2>
              <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#78716c;line-height:1.75;">{a.summary}</p>
            </div>
            <span style="font-size:0.62rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#c4912a;margin-top:auto;">Read Article &rarr;</span>
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <div style="padding:4rem 0;background:#f7f5f0;border-top:1px solid rgba(28,25,23,0.08);">
    <div class="max-w-[1100px] mx-auto px-8" style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;text-align:center;gap:1.25rem;">
      <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:1.25rem;font-style:italic;color:#1c1917;">Want to know which method suits your property?</p>
      <p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#78716c;line-height:1.75;max-width:44ch;">Daniel recommends the sale method that fits the property and the current market, not the one that suits an agent's schedule. Get a straight answer.</p>
      <a href="/get-an-appraisal" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.6rem;padding:0.85rem 1.75rem;background:#c4912a;color:#fff;font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:0.7rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;text-decoration:none;transition:background 0.2s;"
        onmouseover="this.style.background='#a87824'" onmouseout="this.style.background='#c4912a'">
        Get a Free Appraisal
        <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

</article>

</Layout>
